vice故障 → checkoutservice无法获取购物车信息 → frontend下单失败 → 用户收到500错误\n3. **延迟影响**: checkoutservice的GetCart操作延迟激增183倍，成为系统瓶颈\n4. **错误模式**: 所有涉及购物车操作的请求都因cartservice不可用而失败\n\n这个故障的核心是cartservice的DNS解析问题，导致整个下单流程中断。需要重点关注cartservice的网络连接和DNS配置。", "metric_analysis_findings": "{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"io_util\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in server_error_ratio (0.0 to 88.89) and error_ratio (0.0 to 88.89), along with a dramatic rise in rrt (3680.86 to 214728.2) and rrt_max (101677.0 to 2236568.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Metrics show a severe degradation in service performance and reliability.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Elevated error_ratio (0.0 to 0.3) and server_error_ratio (0.0 to 0.3), with increased rrt_max (142771.0 to 1501716.5).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Service performance degradation, though less severe than checkoutservice-0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased error_ratio (0.0 to 0.32) and server_error_ratio (0.0 to 0.32), along with higher rrt_max (136316.5 to 1217722.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Similar performance issues as frontend-0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Rise in server_error_ratio (0.0 to 0.22) and error_ratio (0.0 to 0.22), with increased rrt_max (109371.5 to 209007.5).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Service degradation, though less pronounced than other frontend instances.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Spike in client_error_ratio (0.0 to 51.82) and error_ratio (0.0 to 0.0), with a slight increase in rrt_max (1465.0 to 1541.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Potential issues with client interactions, though less severe than other services.\"\n    },\